snippet.title: SEGA Vintage Collection: ToeJam & Earl (XBLA) - Xbox 360 Gameplay
snippet.description:
Captured off the Xbox One. 

This Xbox Live Arcade compilation brings together both "ToeJam & Earl" and its sequel "ToeJam & Earl in Panic in Funkotron". This 360 release includes the ability to switch between the English and Japanese versions, achievements (200G) and save states. And of course, it's backward compatible on the Xbox One and Series X|S.

SEGA Vintage Collection, SEGA Vintage Collection: ToeJam & Earl (C) SEGA
ToeJam & Earl (C) ToeJam & Earl Productions, Inc.
Developed by M2
Also released as individual titles on PlayStation 3 (PSN)
